00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:10,620
You gotta really
flap 'em hard.

3
00:00:11,070 --> 00:00:12,070
<i>(grunt)</i>

4
00:00:12,920 --> 00:00:13,220
Whoa!

5
00:00:13,230 --> 00:00:14,040
