<i>♪ (celestial theme) </i>

518
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:18,710
Where am I?

519
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:21,030
Not another step.

520
00:20:23,250 --> 00:20:24,950
Princess Luna!

521
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,390
I don't understand.

522
00:20:26,670 --> 00:20:27,580
Where are we?

523
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:29,880
Why did you and
Celestia disappear?

524
00:20:30,230 --> 00:20:33,270
Did you really expect me
to sit idly by

525
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:36,400
while they all basked in
your "precious light"?

526
00:20:36,490 --> 00:20:37,790
"Precious light"?

527
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:41,230
There can only be one
Princess in Equestria.

528
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:45,080
And that Princess
will be me!

529
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:50,710
<i>(cracking)</i>

530
00:20:50,850 --> 00:20:52,320
<i>(explosion)</i>

531
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:54,480
♪

532
00:20:54,490 --> 00:20:58,750
<i>(whistling wind)</i>

533
00:20:58,760 --> 00:21:12,970
♪

534
00:21:16,670 --> 00:21:25,750
<i>(maniacal laughter)</i>

